frames.caption: A solitary figure in a robe stands on a snowy shoreline, gazing at the vibrant aurora borealis dancing across the night sky. The icy landscape is illuminated by the colorful lights and the setting sun, creating a serene and awe-inspiring scene. Snow-covered mountains and a calm, reflective body of water complete the breathtaking view.
frames.description: The scene captures a tranquil winter landscape where a person stands in contemplation, surrounded by the natural beauty of the aurora borealis and snow-covered mountains. The setting sun adds warmth to the otherwise cold environment.
